list.item:
Setting the flag (OP Flags) to CB_OP_AND or CB_OP_SUBDST or CB_OP_MIN,
                    while setting the (SRC flags) to CB_SRC_0 will make the (DST flags)
                    useless.

Setting the flag (OP Flags) to CB_OP_AND or CB_OP_SUBSRC or CB_OP_MIN,
                    while setting the (DST flags) to CB_SRC_0 will make the (SRC flags)
                    useless.

